<plot>A whimsical piece about kids trying to stay cool when the weather gets warm. Based on the silent film model, we follow two young girls as they struggle with financial woes, transportation issues, and bully problems. Nothing will stop them from that ice cream cone. A lighthearted romp through an Austin afternoon, this piece will make you long for your childhood the same way these characters long for a frozen treat.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?246771</url></doc>
